# FastAPI Rules

## Always
- Type hints on every function
- `response_model=` on every endpoint
- `async def` for route handlers
- Pydantic schemas separate from SQLAlchemy models

## Dependency Injection
Use `Depends()` for: database sessions, current user, permissions.

## Never
- Return SQLAlchemy models directly — always use response schemas
- Put business logic in route handlers — use service layer
- Catch-all bare `except:` — be specific
